ntainer\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"980\" height=\"724\" src=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28-1024x756.jpeg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-12296\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28-1024x756.jpeg 1024w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28-300x221.jpeg 300w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28-768x567.jpeg 768w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28-610x450.jpeg 610w, https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2024\/12\/WhatsApp-Image-2024-12-04-at-22.38.28.jpeg 1080w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 980px) 100vw, 980px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<\/section>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-362c126 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"362c126\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bfab0b1 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bfab0b1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_has_onepagescroll_dot&quot;:&quot;yes&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f4127aa elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f4127aa\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;ekit_we_effect_on&quot;:&quot;none&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0px 0px 1em; color: #666666; font-family: Poppins, HelveticaNeue-Light, 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">\u00a0<\/p><h3 style=\"box-sizing: border-box; font-family: Poppins, HelveticaNeue-Light, 'Helvetica Neue Light', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, 'Lucida Grande', sans-serif; clear: both; margin: 1em 0px 0.540791em; color: var(--accent); font-size: 1.618em; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-align: center; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial;\">Itinerary<\/h3><p><b>Day 1: Marrakech \u2013 Kelaat M\u2019Gouna \u2013 Boutaghrar<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Transfer to the Rose Valley: Begin your journey with a scenic drive from Marrakech through the High Atlas Mountains to Kelaat M\u2019Gouna, the gateway to the Rose Valley.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Start the Trek: Meet your guide and trek along picturesque trails to Boutaghrar, a traditional Berber village.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Overnight Stay: Enjoy dinner and stay in a guesthouse, immersing yourself in Berber hospitality.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Day 2: Boutaghrar \u2013 Agouti Gorge \u2013 Tamaloute<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Gorge Trekking: Hike through Agouti Gorge, surrounded by dramatic cliffs and lush vegetation.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Berber Villages: Pass through small, charming villages and interact with locals.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Overnight Camp: Set up camp in Tamaloute, a serene spot amidst the valley\u2019s natural beauty.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Day 3: Tamaloute \u2013 Ait Youl \u2013 Timtda Gorge<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Trail Highlights: Trek along terraced fields and rose gardens, enjoying the fresh scent of roses in bloom.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Explore the Gorge: Hike through the Timtda Gorge, known for its stunning rock formations and peaceful atmosphere.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Overnight Camp: Camp near the gorge, enjoying the tranquility of the area.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Day 4: Timtda Gorge \u2013 Almdoun Plateau \u2013 Hdida Village<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>High Plateau Views: Ascend to the Almdoun Plateau for breathtaking panoramic views of the Rose Valley and the Atlas Mountains.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Descent to Hdida: Trek down to Hdida Village, where you\u2019ll stay in a local guesthouse and enjoy a traditional dinner.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Day 5: Hdida \u2013 Tabarkhach Plateau \u2013 Kelaat M\u2019Gouna<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Final Trek: Cross the Tabarkhach Plateau, taking in the valley&#8217;s stunning scenery one last time.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Return to Kelaat M\u2019Gouna: Arrive in the town known for its rose products and vibrant Rose Festival.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Overnight Stay: Spend the night in a comfortable guesthouse.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Day 6: Kelaat M\u2019Gouna \u2013 Marrakech<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Drive to Marrakech: After breakfast, return to Marrakech, bringing your memorable adventure to a close.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p><b>Highlights of the Trek<\/b><\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Explore the lush Rose Valley, famous for its terraced fields and fragrant roses.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Interact with Berber communities and experience their rich culture and traditions.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Trek through dramatic gorges, high plateaus, and picturesque villages.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Enjoy traditional Moroccan meals and stay in local guesthouses and campsites.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>Take in breathtaking views of the Atlas Mountains and surrounding landscapes.<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>&#8212;<\/p><p>\u00a0<\/p><p>This 6-day trek through the Rose Valley offers a perfect blend of adventure, culture, and natural beauty, leaving you with unforgettable memories of Morocco\u2019s heartland.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Rose Valley trek \u200b Embark on a 6-day trek through Morocco\u2019s enchanting Rose Valley, known for its stunning landscapes, traditional Berber villages, and the fragrant Damask roses that bloom in the spring. This trek offers a perfect combination of adventure, cultural immersion, and natural beauty, making it an unforgettable experience for nature lovers and hikers [&hellip;]<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"parent":11315,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":{"_monsterinsights_skip_tracking":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_active":false,"_monsterinsights_sitenote_note":"","_monsterinsights_sitenote_category":0,"footnotes":""},"class_list":["post-11586","page","type-page","status-publish","hentry"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11586","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=11586"}],"version-history":[{"count":32,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11586\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":12770,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11586\/revisions\/12770"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/11315"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/dunetrektours.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=11586"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}